WEBVTT
NOTE OE3D — Script2 — Hmoob

1
00:00:00.100 --> 00:00:01.484
Nyob zoo!

2
00:00:01.434 --> 00:00:05.222
Koj vừa tau txais koj lub cuab hloov tshiab ntawm Ortho Espace 3D.

3
00:00:05.222 --> 00:00:08.602
Cov hnub thawj yog lub sijhawm tseem ceeb ntawm kev hloov.

4
00:00:08.602 --> 00:00:11.197
Nov yog peb cov lus qhia kom pib tau zoo.

5
00:00:12.597 --> 00:00:14.221
Kev tso rau.

6
00:00:14.171 --> 00:00:18.334
Pib los ntaum lub manchon rau koj lub ceg seem, saib kom tsis muaj kev nkhaus.

7
00:00:18.334 --> 00:00:20.664
Xyuas kom tawv nqaij ncaj nraim.

8
00:00:20.664 --> 00:00:25.114
Tso lub cuab hloov raws li txoj kev txuas ntawm koj lub cuab yeej.

9
00:00:26.514 --> 00:00:28.403
Kev nce sijhawm hnav.

10
00:00:28.353 --> 00:00:31.594
Pib nrog ob teev ib hnub thiab nce zuj zus.

11
00:00:31.594 --> 00:00:34.465
Lub lis piam thawj, sim ncav cuag plaub txog rau teev.

12
00:00:34.465 --> 00:00:38.028
Yog mob tshwm sim, tshem lub cuab hloov tawm thiab hu rau peb.

13
00:00:39.428 --> 00:00:41.119
Koj tawv nqaij li xwm txheej.

14
00:00:41.069 --> 00:00:44.512
Tom qab txhua zaug hnav, xyuas tag nrho lub ceg seem.

15
00:00:44.512 --> 00:00:47.792
Liab me ntsis uas ploj hauv nees nkaum feeb yog ib qho ib txwm muaj.

16
00:00:47.792 --> 00:00:52.887
Tab sis liab txuas ntxiv, qhov raug, los yog pob yog qhia tias yuav tsum mus ntsib kws kho mob.

17
00:00:54.287 --> 00:00:55.974
Kev xyaum dua tshiab.

18
00:00:55.924 --> 00:00:59.791
Kev kho mob rau lub cev yog tseem ceeb heev los rov qab tau kev ywj siab.

19
00:00:59.791 --> 00:01:03.986
Ua hauj lwm ntawm kev npaum, kev taug kev thiab kev txhim kho nqaj nqaij raws koj txoj kev.

20
00:01:03.986 --> 00:01:07.492
Peb pab neeg ntawm Ortho Espace 3D pab tswj koj txoj kev kho mob.

21
00:01:08.892 --> 00:01:12.433
Peb cov kws kho mob nyob kom teb koj cov lus nug.

22
00:01:12.383 --> 00:01:16.135
Tsis txhob ua siab ntsws hu rau peb los yog xa lus hauv WhatsApp.

23
00:01:16.135 --> 00:01:18.411
Sib zog, nej tsis nyob ib leeg!
